      "id": "for-breakdown",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "### Breaking Down the Loop:\n\n```java\nfor (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++)\n```\n\n| Part | Code | Meaning |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Initialization | `int i = 1` | Start counter at 1 |\n| Condition | `i <= 5` | Continue while i is 5 or less |\n| Update | `i++` | Add 1 to i after each loop |\n\n### Execution trace:\n- i=1: Print \"Count: 1\", then i becomes 2\n- i=2: Print \"Count: 2\", then i becomes 3\n- i=3: Print \"Count: 3\", then i becomes 4\n- i=4: Print \"Count: 4\", then i becomes 5\n- i=5: Print \"Count: 5\", then i becomes 6\n- i=6: Condition false (6 is not <= 5), loop ends",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown"
      }
