      "id": "while-intro",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 2. The `while` Loop\n\nUse when you don't know exactly how many times to repeat, but you have a condition to check.\n\n### Syntax:\n```java\nwhile (condition) {\n    // code to repeat\n}\n```\n\nThe loop continues as long as the condition is `true`. Be careful: if the condition never becomes `false`, you'll have an infinite loop!",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown"
      }
    },
