      "id": "do-while-intro",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 3. The `do-while` Loop\n\nSimilar to `while`, but the code runs **at least once** because the condition is checked AFTER the first execution.\n\n### Syntax:\n```java\ndo {\n    // code to repeat (runs at least once)\n} while (condition);\n```\n\n### Key Difference:\n- `while`: Check condition first, then execute\n- `do-while`: Execute first, then check condition",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown"
      }
    },
