      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Loop Control: `break` and `continue`\n\n### `break`\nExits the loop immediately, skipping all remaining iterations.\n\n### `continue`\nSkips the rest of the current iteration and jumps to the next one.",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "break-example",
