      "id": "loop-comparison",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## When to Use Each Loop?\n\n| Loop Type | When to Use |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `for` | Know exact number of iterations |\n| `while` | Don't know iterations, check condition first |\n| `do-while` | Must run at least once, then check condition |\n\n### Quick Decision:\n1. **Know how many times?** Use `for`\n2. **Need to run at least once?** Use `do-while`\n3. **Otherwise?** Use `while`",
